<p>This action displays a customizable pop-up alert to the user. </p>
<h3 id='query-parameters'>Query Parameters</h3>
<table><thead>
<tr>
<th>Key</th>
<th>short-hand</th>
<th>Description</th>
</tr>
</thead><tbody>
<tr>
<td>title</td>
<td>t</td>
<td>The string to display on the button</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>action</td>
<td>a</td>
<td>The action to perform when the button is clicked</td>
</tr>
